description: Enferno Storm Commerce API Client library.
releaseNotes:
What's new?

General:
- #1380 A new Property, Code, has been added to IdValue and it will be populated where appropriate. 

ApplicationService:
- #1380 Code is now available on Store.Info
https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/#/Expose/Entities/IdValue

OrderService:
- #1620 Info field has been added to Order and OrderItem. These info fields will be populated from the corresponding info fields on Basket and BasketItem when the order is created. Only info fields with matching Code will be mapped.
https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/#/Orders/Entities/Info 

- #1380 Code is available on Order.Info and OrderItem.Info.

- #1620 New methods have been added to list OrderInfoTypes.
https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/#/Orders/Operations/ListOrderInfoTypes
https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/#/Orders/Operations/ListOrderItemInfoTypes

ProductService:
- #1380 A new Property, Code, has been added to IdValue and it will be populated where appropriate. Current methods populating this value are ListCategories and ListProductFileTypeIds.
https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/#/Products/Operations/ListCategories
Https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/#/Products/Operations/ListFileTypeIds

- #1380 A new Property, Code, has been added to ProductFile. This values will be shown on Product.Files.

ShoppingService:
- #1380 Code is available on Basket.Info and BasketItem.Info.

- #1629 DoHold has been added to Basket. This Property can be updated in the Checkout process with UpdateBasket.
https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/#/Shopping/Entities/Basket

- #1531. Support internally for decimal as Quantity.


What's fixed?

Miscellaneous changes? 

- #982 AddressLine1 and AddressLine2 has been extended from 100 to 255 characters.

Feedback?
Faults and strange behavior can be reported to support@storm.io or to patrik.rosquist@storm.io.
 
 
Regards,
The Storm API Team
title: Enferno Storm Api Client
